Package cisc187.util

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Queue<E>
    An interface that specifies the familiar queue abstraction, but with limited capacity.
    Stack<E>
    Basic Stack interface
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArrayQueue<E>
    Implements a generic queue of fixed size using a raw array as a backing store.
    ArrayStack<E>
    Implements a generic stack using a raw array as a backing store.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    EmptyQueueException
    Thrown by the peek and dequeue methods of a Queue when there is nothing in the Queue.
    EmptyStackException
    Thrown by the peek method of a Stack when there is nothing in the Stack to observe.
    FullQueueException
    Thrown by the enqueue method of a Queue when the Queue is full.
